The Authorize.Net  Payment Gateway can help you accept credit card and electronic check payments quickly and affordably. More than 305,000 merchants trust them for payment processing and online fraud prevention solutions.

What can I do with it?
This class is a wrapper written in PHP5 that can be used to submit credit card transactions to the Authorize.net payment gateway using the AIM Web services API. The class provides functions for setting the payment details like the customer name, address, phone number, shipping address, charge amount, credit card number and expiry date.

How do I use it?
First you'll need to have an account with Authorize.Net if you don't already have one. Download this class and plugin in the information that you want to submit. An example is included.